lead_paragraph: Barcelona will put Manchester City to the sword if they commit the same kind of errors as they did in their Champions League encounter last month, coach Luis Enrique has said.

headline.print_headline: Barcelona Will Punish City Errors, Warns Enrique
headline.main: Barcelona Will Punish City Errors, Warns Enrique
